headline: Analog stock targets raised at Mizuho ahead of Q2 earnings
summary: Investing.com -- Mizuho raised price targets across a slate of analog semiconductor names ahead of June-quarter earnings, citing signs of bottoming in the auto-industrial cycle and improving pricing dynamics for the second half of 2025.
